        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Thanks CD for comments on his fern paper [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">3847</hi> and <hi rend="doubleUnderline">3853</hi>]; has great difficulty in expressing his ideas.</p> 
            <p>Discusses inheritance and variation.</p>
            <p>Asks CD for an account of the experiments he would like JS to perform.</p>
        </abstract>
